Millburn High School girls volleyball program holding car wash October 14, 2015 Last updated: Wednesday, October 14, 2015, 4:03 PM The Item of Millburn and Short Hills 
girls volleyball 
Millburn spikers holding car wash, bake sale Oct. 17 
Millburn High School's girls volleyball program is scheduled to hold a car wash and bake sale Saturday, Oct. 17, from 9 a.m. to 2 p.m. in the driveway located in front of the school. 
The school is located at 462 Millburn Ave. 
Proceeds from the car wash and bake sale will help support the program's varsity, junior varsity and freshman teams. Â© 2015 North Jersey Media Group Tags:
